### RLS 정책
```sql
-- 읽기: 모두 허용
CREATE POLICY "Public read access"
  ON table_name FOR SELECT
  USING (true);

-- 쓰기: 인증된 사용자만
CREATE POLICY "Authenticated users can insert"
  ON table_name FOR INSERT
  WITH CHECK (auth.uid() = user_id);
```

